OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FAre arsonists behind       
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FItaly's devastating        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fwildfires?                 
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Wildfires have been raging in parts of 
OL,6, southern Italy recently - forcing      
OL,7, thousands to flee. Many are blamed on  
OL,8, arsonists.                             
OL,10,FAgricultural union Coldiretti suggests 
OL,11,Fup to 60% of wildfires are man-made.   
OL,12,FBut why would anybody provoke a deadly 
OL,13,Ffire?                                  
OL,15,FLocals in Calabria tell the BBC that   
OL,16,Feveryone from clumsy farmers to feuding
OL,17,Fneighbours are to blame for the blazes.
OL,19,FThe severe heat and drought, worsened  
OL,20,Fby climate change, only make matters   
OL,21,Fworse.                                 
